::Iron Fist::

The bay's hatch closed behind Angel Prime as he was pushed in, 
several sirens going off as the Maximal signauture was detected 
inside. Autoguns flipped down from the cealing, rows of them aiming 
themselves at Angel Prime. The hatch magnetically locked, three more 
doors magneticaly locking themselves in front of it. The only other 
exit locked in the same fashion, with three doors in front of it. The 
many autoguns swirled around to aim at Angel Prime, flamethrowers 
imbedded in several sections of the walls ready. There was no escape.

The autoguns opened fire.
